Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: I am in the channel and it is still active. But it is a shame that this project has not lived to the expectations. I am following them from almost the start. The product they are developing is something actually needed in European markets and has huge potential.  BUT, from the begging they have been struggling with the marketing, they failed to raise money in the hype time when their ICO was ongoing. And the biggest fail regarding their marketing strategy was the re branding to API token, I mean why the hell you would call your token API token?! This name automatically is a no for anyone looking to invest or speculate on the token price. Yes, it is correct that token is used for API payments . There are thousands of tokens which are used only for specific reason in small ecosystem, but they do not go and sink their potential by re branding their token name to some kind of technical token.

Author: Karamen35
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Our main intention is to create Bank as a Service (BaaS) platform for fintech developers that will be able to get access to our infrastructure and customer base via API. Developers with small or medium capital will be able to create their fintech apps and enter the banking market without the need to establish the whole infrastructure and getting banking license by themselves. It substantially reduces barriers to enter the market, which are currently very high.

Author: maardhayrule
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Everyone, if you are seing  this ICO as a get rich quick as few ICOs were you should have invested in other projects. Give time for the team  to do their work and you will see  the Token value jump positive. We  could be listed  in a Top 15 Exchange and still have no  volume as you have it today.  So dont judge the project before it  is  born. Give FSB time to leverage their awareness and than you'll see the value go up. And if you  bought  into  the ICO at 4$, dont consider it an loss.  Give them time. Comparing  to other  ICO the total volume is mid-low, so if  the team falls through with leveraging awareness, keeping to their roadmap and list on exchanges we will see the value sky rocket.  And remmeber most of Top 15 echanges require large sums to list tokens in. And I prefer seing this grow organically and not waste money, than  seing them invest 1M$ to get listed on Binance and fail to have a budget to leverage interest in the Project itself.

Author: camargoherrera
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: The projects that are in the same field as we do are Bankera, and Babb, but we dont see them as competitors, because they have different approach and diffterent services to offer.We are a developer oriented bank, that will serve as a fintech distribution platform for applications brought to it. Say we don't have a microcredit service, but you offer one. Using our API, you can bring your microcredit application to our bank, using our infrastructure and we will advertise to our clients. We will work on revenue share model. So the main difference is that we will have a core set of mandatory services and an API that will allow to connect other services to our bank as modules.

Author: jamzzz123
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: I had managed to translate it using google, whereby you can translate the whole page. It's worth doing and having a read as there is some interesting information.  I have quoted the article below translated.  Quote  Compliance with regulations is important, but not something engineers should deal with — it would only hamper innovation. Read up on this issue in reports by Chinese media on our efforts.  Compliance is important, but it is not handled by engineers - it only hinders innovation. You can continue to understand this topic from another Chinese media report on our efforts.  The latest wave of financial technology may change traditional systems and improve the lives of consumers, but promising small start-ups are hampered by complex compliance laws, rules, and regulations before they begin operations. A new European start-up company has provided a solution to this global problem, which is also an important factor for the Chinese market.  Financial technology is an irresistible force, but now it is facing an irrevocable target: compliance with regulations. Talented small financial technology development teams may come up with groundbreaking technologies, but before they bring them to market, they will have to hire a team of lawyers to ensure that they comply with national financial and consumer laws. New ventures with transnational ambitions must go through this process as they enter each new market and economic region.  Alexander Mullins discovered the problem and decided to do something about it. His company, Forty Seven Bank, allows developers to create new technologies under their protection and provide them with access to all bank licenses so that they can fully comply with the regulations in any market they operate. "Engineers and founders should not focus on things like compliance, risk management or building customer service organizations. If we do these things for them, they can focus on what they are good at and sell their products in parallel." Marlins said.

Author: Serenar
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: The projects that are in the same field as we do are Bankera, and Crypterium, but we dont see them as competitors, because they have different approach and diffterent services to offer.We are a developer oriented bank, that will serve as a fintech distribution platform for applications brought to it. Say we don't have a microcredit service, but you offer one. Using our API, you can bring your microcredit application to our bank, using our infrastructure and we will advertise to our clients. We will work on revenue share model. So the main difference is that we will have a core set of mandatory services and an API that will allow to connect other services to our bank as modules.

Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Here is some helpful information on when/requirements of getting listed on coinmarketcap  What is the criteria for a cryptocurrency to be listed on CoinMarketCap?  The criteria for a cryptocurrency to be listed is the following:  - Must be a cryptocurrency or a crypto token. - Must be on a public exchange with an API that reports the last traded price and the last 24 hour trading volume. - Must have a non-zero trading volume on at least one supported exchange so a price can be determined. - For market cap ranking, an accurate circulating supply figure is required.

Author: Anilg
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Main main part of the FSBT project -  FSBT will develop all the infrastructure and authorize it at Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) in the United Kingdom. Developers with small or medium capital will be able to create their fintech apps and upload them to FSBT app platform and get access to our infrastructure and client base via API. By doing that FSBT will reduce barriers to entry into the banking market which are currently very high and banking sector is controlled by traditional banks who are very slow in terms of innovation. FSBT will disrupt this, introduce new competition from fintech developers who will be able to create even their own White Label banks using FSBT platform.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: The bigger exchanges have bigger trading volumes, and the coins and tokens that are listed are with real products and already a large number of customers. Also biggest exchange points have a lot more requirements to list, such as: -New blockchain features -A significant improvement over existing blockchain -Interesting, innovative, or unique application -Usefulness of use cases -Technological experience and reputation of the token applicant and team -Market interest We have these points, so we have a very good chance to get into bigger exchanges. Smaller ones dont need so much requirements

The domestic largest enterprises are leading the industry exclusively. Even though this brings good results in the short term, we have the risk that in the long term there will be further holdbacks on the growth of the entire Finetec world. Under such circumstances, we will aim to offer "Innovative FinTech Solutions" that can be implemented without relying on large companies and large-scale budgets as we enter Japan. Author: phantam
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: No it doesn't energy is not a restriction on crypto, mining is not a "crypto" thing, its just one way of handling concensus, theirs a large number of ways to handle it that are much more power efficient and hell even for mining their are more energy efficient ways (see burstcoin).  The fact is even ethereum is on its way to moving away from mining to proof of stake, which will mean all that power being used for ethereum will shift to another coin, but the fact is at that point ethereum will be no where near  as electricity hungry as it currently is.  Mining coins will remain but, the fact is mining won't be the reason fiat survives. Eventually their will be fiat replacements, thare basically Proof Of Stake or some other hybrid Proof of XXXXXX, and you'll be able to just run mobile wallets, perhaps even banks like 47bk will run masternodes for said currency as well as other banks to maintain consensus and everyone will instead of fiat just use a phone with NFC to pay their bills.  You have to remember FIAT has had its days numbered in the physical form for a long time, its already rare in some areas to see it due to the large prevelence of Debit/Credit cards and payment apps. Crypto is just the next evolution of that removing the centralized banks/credit companies.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: FSBT token holders will have the following important benefits:  1) They will become the first clients of Forty Seven Bank;  2) The rights to be the first to try and use products and services offered by Forty Seven Bank;  3) Top priority place in Forty Seven Bank loyalty program;  4) Opportunity to contribute to the development of crypto community and help in charity campaigns;  5) Discounts and special conditions for products and services of Forty Seven Bank;  6) Higher FSBL token cashback multiplier when paying with Forty Seven Bank debit or credit card;  7) The range of the most commonly used mobile and online banking products for free;  No fee for using Multi-Asset Account;  9) Opportunity to sell tokens more expensively on secondary market when they increase in value in future;  10) Possibility for traders to speculate on token yield.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: We have special benefits structure after we get a banking license. The structure of these benefits is based on the amount of contribution during ICO. In order to get them, a person will have to become the bank’s client and then go through Know Your Customer (KYC) procedure.  If a person contributes between 0.1 and 1 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments.  If a person contributes between 1 and 5 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Classic credit card that will be sent via mail.  If a person contributes between 5 and 10 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.) investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 25% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first two years.   If a person contributes between 10 and 50 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 30% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first three years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first year.  If a person contributes between 50 and 100 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 50% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first five years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first three years; Special conditions for trading activities.  If a person contributes between 100 and more ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 50% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first ten years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first five years; Special conditions for trading activities; No commission and fees for using any banking products and services of Forty Seven Bank for ever (except loans).

Author: Anilg
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: I found some interesting information about FSBT -  Mainly for individuals is connected to Payment Services Directive 2 (PSD2) which comes into force this year in the EU. The directive obliges all the EU banks to open access to their infrastructure via API for third parties. And FSBT going to take advantage of this issue and create so called Multi-Asset Account - a product (an application) which will allow you to get to all your accounts in different banks, to all your cryptowallets and to all your investments. You will be able to manage all your finances, transfer funds here and there by using only one single application - it will make life easier and more effective.  FSBT really one of the interesting project in recent times.

Author: phantam
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Etherdeltas security issues were minor in the grand scope of things, if your really worried about getting phished just record the contract address on etherdelta, and make sure your always using the real smartcontract address to handle transactions and trades. The fact is in comparison to others EtherDelta and exchanges like it are actually the most secure of all exchanges because their is no middle man playing with your money, just a public smart contract that anyone can review.  Where etherdelta and exchanges may have issues to exploit is in their frontend GUI (website), but technically theirs nothing forcing you to use the GUI, just learn how to use the smartcontract directly and your truely 100% safe .

Author: jamzzz123
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: The mission of Forty Seven Bank is to create innovative, flexible and open Application Platform for financial technology developers, who will be able to operate under the roof of Forty Seven Bank, having access to banks infrastructure and customer base. We will give the opportunity to developers with small or medium capital to create white label applications which will be able to compete with traditional banks. Our Bank as a Service (BaaS) solution will disrupt the financial sector of the European Union by reducing barriers to entry the fintech market.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: We are planning to develop Forty Seven Bank App Platform that will become heaven for fintech developers, as they will be able to create fintech applications and use umbrella services of the bank (KYC, AML, our customer base, etc.). It means that developers with small or medium amount of capital will be able to create White Label business powered by infrastructure of Forty Seven Bank. A good analogy is Apple and App Store that is a heaven for mobile developers. In our case, in order for a developer to do this, he will need FSBT tokens. Moreover, we are going to offer businesses the opportunity to improve the effectiveness of financial and operational activities via smart contracts. Again, to do this, they will need FSBT. These two things are going to create real demand for FSBT on secondary market. Apart from that, token holders will be top priority clients of the bank and according to loyalty program will receive portion of Forty Seven Bank net profit every year in a form of FSBL loyalty tokens which can be later exchanged to wide range of various products and services (travelling, electronic, clothing, gift cards, etc.). Imagine a loyalty program in a retail store where you have a card and every time you make a purchase, you get some points which can be later exchanged for something. FSBL/FSBT token yield will be quite small in the beginning, as it is connected to performance of the bank, but under the conditions and calculations for our hardcap of 10M EUR, in 2023 token yield will be 167% - in other words - for each ETH contributed during ICO in 2023 you will get bonusin FSBL tokens equal to 1.67 ETH. Token yield will grow every year and our performance will inflate the price of the token substantially. I offer you to read more about this in our document called Token Holders Benefits: https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BwDjfDDrGhcsLTJOYzd1ZkZ0WU0/view

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Talking about unsold tokens - they will not be generated. We generate tokens which we sell, no more, no less, so there is nothing to be burned.

I've actually had a few seriously ideas about identity based blockchains for not just biometrics but all personal information, the fact is oneway hashes especially if combined with another layer of encryption is insanely secure if developed properly.  People are afraid of a biometric db getting hacked behind oneway keys and encryption, yet give all their biometrics and data to equifax who stored all their data in an unencrypted open unlocked database and continues to do so, many of the things you think of secure from the old days isn't and is just waiting to get broken. Blockchain stands to resolve much of that.

Author: rezzx
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: There are safe ways to store sensitive data such as fingerprints and other biometric data. Usually the data is hashed and only the hash is stored in the servers. This way if the servers are hacked, there isn't much to do with the hash since you can't produce the original data with it, only validate it.

Body: We have had rather slow beginning, as our ICO structure is a little bit different than others have - our ICO lasts till 31st of March and in the first round we have been trying different activities to find out what works better. By doing that we have attracted around 1400+ ETH equivalent. Now, when we are very well presented in press and on ICO listings (major are still to come) we are going to launch substantial campaign. There is no doubt we will reach our soft cap, most probably even this week and we are not going to slow down our progress, the final goal is to reach hard cap. Talking about unsold tokens - they will not be generated

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: We are planning to be listed on several major exchanges right after the end of ICO, which is officially on 31st of March. However, as we plan to reach our hard cap earlier, we will finish ICO process earlier as well, so most probably FSBT will hit the exchanges in February-March.  At first we are planning to be listed on HitBTC, Binance and EtherDelta, later we are planning also to be listed on Bittrex and Poloniex (may be more).  Currently we begin negotiations with several exchanges.  Tokens are generated when we receive contirbutions and there will be as much tokens generated as much contributions we receive + 5% for bounties and +5% for founders after the end of ICO.  Talking about ICO period - we have decided to make it that long in order to be able to become very well-known in cryptocurrency world and attract as many contributors as possible. During the first stages of ICO we have been trying different PR and marketing options and now we know very well what to do in terms of promotion and are about to begin the main part of our promotional campaign. Currently there are several ICOs that last that long, some of them even longer. The market is changing and ICO structures are also changing. In any case, if everything goes, as planned (if we receive more and more substantial contributons and will be sure in ICO success), we will begin working on our product before the end of ICO investing our own money into the project.

Author: vireal
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: December 17, 2017  Dear bounty hunters, after several discussions with active community members and pure statistical analysis of the numbers we’ve gathered so far, we’ve decided to tweak our bounty campaign, so that it would better suit our project's goals and reflect the reality of what Bitcointalk has to offer.  Change list Community management campaign FSBT-pool changed from 20% to 10%. Translations Campaign FSBT-pool changed from 15% to 20%. Media support campaign Campaign is removed (merged with Blogging campaign), it’s 10% FSBT-pool is redistributed among other campaigns. Blogging campaign FSBT-pool changed from 5% to 20%; All participants' entries from Media support campaign have been reregistered to Blogging campaign; New entry added: Share article on Facebook + Tweet → +25 points; Facebook campaign FSBT-pool changed from 4% to 10%. Twitter campaign FSBT-pool changed from 4% to 10%. Bug tracking campaign FSBT-pool changed from 5% to 3%. Unique support campaign Campaign is removed, it’s 10% FSBT-pool is redistributed among other campaigns.  Incase you have any questions regarding this change, please join our official bounty campaign Telegram group, we would be glad to answer them.[/list][/list]

Laws are change, banking and exchange systems differ from each other. In that scenario, bridging between traders, businessmen and user is most important and much needed. This project came with complete solution for individual, traders, and businessmen and also government’s institutions. This project will be very convenient for all. One more major issue is to exchange crypto to fiat in different countries. They get the services but pay very heavy fees. Do you have any solution for this problem?  Although you have described very briefly but I could not get this solution in your given details. Thanks team

Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: If a person contributes between 0.1 and 1 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments.  If a person contributes between 1 and 5 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Classic credit card that will be sent via mail.  If a person contributes between 5 and 10 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.) investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 25% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first two years.  If a person contributes between 10 and 50 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), invest- ments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 30% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first three years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first year.  If a person contributes between 50 and 100 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 50% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first five years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first three years; Special conditions for trading activities.  If a person contributes between 100 and more ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 50% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first ten years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first five years; Special conditions for trading activities; No commission and fees for using any banking products and services of Forty Seven Bank for ever (except loans).   Are those "prepaid" visa cards where you can only spend what is backed by your account or do you have a real credit sum?

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Business will have to go through standard KYC and AML procedures in order to open a bank account. In our case we will make a bank with remote identification, where a client will be able to  go through these procedures right via personal cabinet. After that, the client will get access to API and will be able to create his own web applications or bots or anything else.  Taking into account that all the critical data will be stored at our side, on the basis of our API our clients will have opportunity to concentrate on the development of their business and marketing. Developers will get commissions as technical service providers for customer attraction in convenient way for them - either in fiat or cryptocurrencies.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Hard cap for ICO is 360 000 ETH, according to our calculations it will be approximately 100M FSBT tokens (including bonus tokens). Hard cap for pre-ICO is 90 000 ETH.  There is no real softcap, we will launch the project either way, as we do have interested institutional and private investors. All the contributors to our project will receive FSBT tokens and benefits stated in our documents. If we do not get enough ETH during ICO, we will get necessary funding partly from our investors, partly from our own resources.  Minimum amount is stated as our estimate of how much funds we need to begin the project and provide the range of products and services described for Milestone 1. However, we believe our ICO procedure will help us to gather much more resources than 18 000 ETH and we will start with bigger capital and will become more successful.   Also, there are many bank projects, how do you compete with them?  There is no bank working with cryptocurrencies on the same level as with fiat, whereas banks of the future will have to adjust to changing evroinment. Forty Seven Bank will be a pioneer in this field by taking a leading position among the banks of the future. So, we don't have competitors.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: If a person contributes between 0.1 and 1 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments.  If a person contributes between 1 and 5 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Classic credit card that will be sent via mail.  If a person contributes between 5 and 10 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.) investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 25% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first two years.  If a person contributes between 10 and 50 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), invest- ments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 30% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first three years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first year.  If a person contributes between 50 and 100 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 50% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first five years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first three years; Special conditions for trading activities.  If a person contributes between 100 and more ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 50% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first ten years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first five years; Special conditions for trading activities; No commission and fees for using any banking products and services of Forty Seven Bank for ever (except loans).

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Having your own cryptocurrency is not the main thing and it is far from being that.  Traditional banks in Europe are facing serious advantages related to introduction of Payment Services Directive 2 (PSD2) which obliges the banks to reconstruct their infrastructure in order to grant access to their data for third parties via API. For traditional banks with millions of clients and accounts it is very complex procedure which is much more expensive and time consuming if to compare with financial technology start-ups which can build everything from scratch.  Being a pioneer in this field, Forty Seven Bank is going to take leading position in short period of time and become the most recognizable financial institution for crypto world and traditional finance world demanding innovative, user friendly and cost efficient banking products and services.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Yes, that's exactly what is meant by White Label banking. This opportunity arises with introduction of Payment Services Directive 2 (PSD2) introduced by the European Commission that comes into force in January, 2018.

All the contributors to our project will receive FSBT tokens and benefits stated in our documents. If we do not get enough ETH during ICO, we will get necessary funding partly from our investors, partly from our own resources. Taking into account that our team already has experience of licensing financial institutions in FCA, the UK, we believe that we will replicate the experience and get the banking license on time - we know how to do it, what are the requirements and procedures, as well as we do know lots of details that are not clear to others, who do not have this experience.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: At the moment we see three possible applications for boimetric technology - biometric POS terminals, smart ATMs and boimetric authentications for financial apps on mobile phones. In every case this technology will be used to simplify the process of authentication for the end user and replace the use of passwords and PIN codes. The user will be able to decide whether he or she allows to use this technology to access his account and even set the limits and restrictions on transactions with this type of authorization. The protection of biometric data begins with scanner hardware that receives biometric data. Forty Seven Bank will not produce such hardware, but we will cooperate with companies which does. We will carefully evaluate the protection of biometrical devices and will work with most trusted and secure vendors and technologies on the market. Biometrical devices usually has some kind of hardware-level protection against data theft and intrusion, in some cases biometrical data is stored in protected internal memory and will be not transmitted to the server in form of biometric data. In such cases our software will securelly authenticate the device and transfer the sensitive user data in form of cryptographically protected tokens. In other cases the biometric data will be transmitted to our servers and then match against samples stored in secure infrastructure of Forty Seven Bank. All information will be transfered in encrypted form over network. We will also develop and use special software for detection of anomalies and intrusion in order to detect fraudulent activity and the use of stolen data. Also we will develop and publish the recommendations for secure POS terminal installation on merchant side - suggest to install surveillance, access control and biometric authentication systems for their employees to protect terminals from installation of malware.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Investors will become FSBT token holders of our Bank. Tokens will be transfered to contributors' Ethereum wallets by a smart contract in conformity with the donation amount and the bonuses defined in the bonus system.  Token holders of FSBT tokens will get several important benefits:  1) They will be top priority clients of Forty Seven Bank and will receive yearly rewards in FSBL tokens that can be exchanged in our loyalty shop for wide range of different products and services, such as travelling, electronics, entertainment, clothing, etc. Forty Seven Bank will invest 20% of its net profit for previous year into loyalty program. The figure below describes this.  https://i.imgur.com/67GuVqK.png  2) Token holders will be the first to try our products and services.  3) Developers and businesses who have FSBT tokens will be able to get full access to Forty Seven Bank products and services and will be able to upload their applications on Forty Seven App Platform or build automated business powered by blockchain and smart contract technologies.  These are the main benefits, but there are more of them.  Apart from that, contributors to our ICO campaign will get additional benefits from Forty Seven Bank based on the amount of their contribution.  You can find more information about this in our document Token Holders Benefits following this link:   https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BwDjfDDrGhcsLTJOYzd1ZkZ0WU0/view

Depending on milestone reached during ICO procedure we will have amount of capital that will allow us to begin with different range of products and services. You can learn more about our milestones and product introduction stages in our White Paper (starting with page #53) following this link:   https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BzvESRkgX-uDeHc1QjRzbHRBelU/view Let us know if you need any further information!

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Forty Seven Bank is not just cryptocurrency bank. Our concept is to build the bridge between cryptocurrency world and traditional monetary systems - to unite financial operations with crytocurrencies and fiat currencies under one roof. We will offer traditional banking products and services, as well as similar services for cryptocurrencies which are currently not being offered by any other bank. There is no bank working with cryptocurrencies on the same level as with fiat, whereas banks of the future will have to adjust to changing evroinment. Forty Seven Bank will be a pioneer in this field by taking a leading position among the banks of the future.

Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers

Body: It is not necessary, you can simply contribute funds from your ETH wallet. However, we believe it is better to register on our web-page and in our cabinet which will soon be available in order to see balance of your FSBT tokens and all other analytics related to it.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Multi-Asset Account does not have IBAN by itself. It is a term used for a product - an application - that combies all your IBANs in different EU banks via API (also IBAN at Forty Seven Bank). This opportunity is presented by Payment Services Directive 2 (PSD2) which comes into force in Europe in the beginning of next year. You will be able to transfer funds among these IBANs via one application - you will not have to access each internet or mobile bank separately, as it is being done today. Additionally, in this application you will have access to crypto wallets and investments.

Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers

The figure below describes this.  https://i.imgur.com/67GuVqK.png  2) Token holders will be the first to try our products and services.  3) Developers and businesses who have FSBT tokens will be able to get full access to Forty Seven Bank products and services and will be able to upload their applications on Forty Seven App Platform or build automated business powered by blockchain and smart contract technologies.  These are the main benefits, but there are more of them.  Apart from that, contributors to our ICO campaign will get additional benefits from Forty Seven Bank based on the amount of their contribution.  You can find more information about this in our document Token Holders Benefits following this link:   https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BwDjfDDrGhcsLTJOYzd1ZkZ0WU0/view"

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: All ICO participants will receive benefits in terms of using products and services of Forty Seven Bank. The structure of these benefits is based on the amount of contribution during ICO. In order to get them, a person will have to become the bank’s client and then go through Know Your Customer (KYC) procedure.  If a person contributes between 0.1 and 1 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments.  If a person contributes between 1 and 5 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Classic credit card that will be sent via mail.  If a person contributes between 5 and 10 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 25% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first two years.  If a person contributes between 10 and 50 ETH, he gets:      years; Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 30% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first three years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first year.  If a person contributes between 50 and 100 ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 50% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first five years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first three years; Special conditions for trading activities.  If a person contributes between 100 and more ETH, he gets: Free Multi-Asset Account: IBAN (EUR, USD, etc.), crypto wallets (BTC, ETH, etc.), investments; Free Visa Platinum credit card that will be sent via mail; 50% discount on personal and travel insurance for contributor and two family members during the first ten years; No commission on cash withdrawal in any ATM in the world during the first five years; Special conditions for trading activities; No commission and fees for using any banking products and services of Forty Seven Bank for ever (except loans).

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Forty Seven Bank will provide the escrow service as a smart contract. In case of sale deal between customers, this contract will protect both the seller and the buyer. Both customers can work with this contract either via bank user interface or integrate their IT systems directly to escrow smart contract via blockchain. The smart contract defines the following interaction between counterparties: ● Buyer initiates purchase via smart contract; ● Forty Seven Bank locks the needed funds in the buyer’s account; ● Seller delivers the product; ● Buyer within limited time period inspects the product and accepts or rejects the deal; ● If the deal is accepted then funds are transferred to seller’s, account, otherwise, they are unlocked in buyer’s account.  Additionally, we will provide escrow services for ICO and other projects where those might be integrated.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: The debit card from customer and merchant perspective will work like usual Visa or Mastercard debit card. The customer may decide to which type of account the debit card is bound when he or she signs an aggreement with Forty Seven Bank. It can be bound to Multi-Asset Account, fiat account, crypto-stable currency account or cryptocurrency wallet. First of all, the bank will check whether customer has enough funds and will approve transaction if customer has sufficient amount of funds in his account and simultaneously will lock these funds.  After that, funds either are withdrawn directly from fiat account or equivalent amount of cryptocurrency is withdrawn from customer cryptocurrency wallet. Funds may be converted between cryptocurrency and fiat currency using current exchange rate. Bank will have own nodes in major blockchains such as Bitcoin and Ethereum, store the customer wallet keys and manage customer wallets. So, there will be no problem for the bank to execute these transactions on behalf of our customers directly in blockchain.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Business will have to go through standard KYC and AML procedures in order to open a bank account. In our case we will make a bank with remote identification, where a client will be able to  go through these procedures right via personal cabinet. After that, the client will get access to API and will be able to create his own web applications or bots or anything else. Taking into account that all the critical data will be stored at our side, on the basis of our API our clients will have opportunity to concentrate on the development of their business and marketing. Developers will get commissions as technical service providers for customer attraction in convenient way for them - either in fiat or cryptocurrencies.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Forty Seven Bank will build comprehensive and multi-layered security system to protect the assets and privacy of our client. We will develop and execute set of internal security policies that will cover such areas as: - financial protection: - maintaining reserves, - hedging risks, - physical protection of assets and important paper documents: - safes & vaults, - access control and monitoring, - NDA contracts with employees, - office entrance control system, - surveillance system, - regular security audits, - electronic protection of digital data and information: - data replication to several geographically distributed locations, - data encryption for stored data and communication over public networks, - network level security using firewalls and VPN, - operating system security and regular security updates, - digital signatures for important digital documents, - multi-signature for important transactions, - cold offline wallets for cryptocurrency, - intrusion detection system, - two-factor authentication for customers, - fraud detection, - protection agains DDoS attacks.

Author: FortySeven
Title: [ANN] 💠 FSBT TECH 💠 – Open API For Fintech Developers
Body: Thank you for your question! Of course, Forty Seven Bank will provide full range of traditional banking products, as well as products and services for crypto world. One of our featured products will be Multi-Asset Account. According to Payment Services Directive 2 (PSD2) that comes into force in the beginning of next year, all EU banks have to grant access to their APIs to third party service providers. It means, that you will be able to have an access to all the accounts in different banks via one application. In our case - having Multi-Asset Account you will have the access to all your bank accounts, crypto wallets, investments in different assets (stocks, bonds, commodities, etc.) - in one application. And, of course, Multi-Asset Account will be connected to a card - Classic, Platinum or Infinite.
